    "en": {
      "title": "18hr Water Cut during weekend for multiple areas",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); The National Water Supply and Drainage Board (NWSDB) says that the water supply will be interrupted for 18 hours for several areas in the Colombo Districts from 8.00 AM on 3rd of September (Saturday) to 2.00 AM on 4th September (Sunday) 2022.",
        "The water cut will affect the Colombo, Dehiwela \u2013 Mt. Lavinia, Kotte, and Kaduwela M.C areas, Maharagama, Boralasgamuwa, Kolonnawa U. C. areas, Kotikawatta Mulleriyawa P. S. areas, Rathmalana and Katubedda.",
        "One-month-old infant abandoned at a motor garage with a letter",
        "Are you a victim of Cyber Crime? Police Unit ready to crackdown crime in the cyberspace"
      ],
